pharmaceutical companies, reaching even as far as Australia and North America.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-75b1c43 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"75b1c43\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Paperless Conferences<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a2eb7c7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a2eb7c7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Micepad aims to pave the way towards a modern way of conducting MICE events with our software and event support. Our mobile solution caters not only to the tech-savvy generation but also to the older generation through our user-friendly interface. Gone are the days when last-minute printing and stacks of event materials are the norms. With Micepad, companies can reduce their carbon footprint, making a difference not only to the environment but also to the richness of information they gather through each event.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ac82bef elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ac82bef\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Customised Design<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ea9c21c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ea9c21c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p